title: Rhein Gibson leads Web.com Tour Finals finale
text: Rhein Gibson leads Web.com Tour Finals finale Thursday, 1 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) PONTE VEDRA BEACH, Fla. (AP) " Rhein Gibson shot a 7-under 63 on Thursday to take a one-stroke lead in the Web.com Tour Finals-ending Web.Com Tour Championship.The Australian had eight birdies and a bogey on Dye's Valley Course...
